OL,3,CSummer holidays hit by inflation - as
OL,4,Chospitality prices are up 5% year on
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe hospitality trade faces rising
OL,8,Foverheads including Labour and energy,
OL,9,Fso despite the need to attract
OL,10,Fcustomers, many have been forced to
OL,11,Fincrease their prices.
OL,13,FHotels are caught in an inflation
OL,14,Fdilemma: their costs have risen but
OL,15,Fhard-pressed holidaymakers are using
OL,16,Fevery trick in the book to get
OL,17,Fdiscounts.
