OL,3,CSummer holidays hit by inflation - as
OL,4,Chospitality prices are up 5% year on
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FMany other aspects of a good holiday
OL,8,Fare also affected by todays inflation
OL,9,Ffigures, including recreation and
OL,10,Fculture where prices are up around 4%
OL,11,Fannually.
OL,13,FAlcohol and tobacco, another feature
OL,14,Fof many holidays, are up over 7%.
OL,16,FWhilst today's rise in inflation was
OL,17,Fbroadly predicted, it remains lower
OL,18,Fthan European neighbours like France
OL,19,Fand Germany.
